Package com.cafean.client.ui.message

Class ModelErrorReport

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.client.ui.message.ModelErrorReport
  • public class ModelErrorReport
extends java.lang.Object
    A container for the errors, warnings, messages, etc., that result from performing a check model or check stream.
    See Also:
    Message, MessageGroup, CategoryMessageGroup
